289
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,110
Jiang Yi.

290
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:13,590
Jiang Yi.

291
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:17,350
Jiang Yi.

292
00:23:17,350 --> 00:23:18,790
