295
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,680
Yingzi manages to get the offer!

296
00:23:55,830 --> 00:23:56,920
Yi.

297
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:58,070
Are you asleep?

298
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:04,110
