for a short while.

307
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:43,310
Yet, you managed to get a good score.

308
00:24:43,310 --> 00:24:45,270
This means that you have potential.

309
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:48,000
When you're in the UK,

310
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:50,200
I'll make sure you
get admitted to a good college.

311
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,750
Then, you can study hard.

312
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,830
You'll grow up to be a capable man.

313
00:24:57,550 --> 00:24:58,880
When did I agree to go to the UK?

314
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,830
I'm

315
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,550
discussing it with you.

316
00:25:06,030 --> 00:25:08,070
I wondered why you came back.

317
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,110
You're waiting for me
to fail my studies,

318
00:25:09,110 --> 00:25:09,880
so you can use it as an excuse

319
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:11,400
to take me to the UK.

320
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,350
No.

321
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:14,830
That's not what I meant.

322
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:16,680
How could you say that?

323
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:17,270
We're

324
00:25:17,270 --> 00:25:19,510
truly concern about your future.

325
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:20,880
If you couldn't get into college,

326
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:21,750
what do you do?

327
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:22,790
That's my own business.

328
00:25:22,790 --> 00:25:24,160
It's none of your business!

329
00:25:29,350 --> 00:25:31,030
I won't ever go to the UK.

330
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,510
Calm down, Yi.

331
00:25:32,510 --> 00:25:33,750
Listen carefully.

332
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:35,070
You can't be so stubborn about this.

333
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:35,550
That's enough.

334
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:37,070
Stop it.

335
00:25:40,750 --> 00:25:41,680
Please leave.

336
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,270
Please.

337
00:25:48,720 --> 00:25:49,960
I'll talk to you again.

338
00:25:51,030 --> 00:25:51,880
Drink the milk.

339
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,960
Why are you acting like my parents?

340
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,830
I didn't get admitted
to a top college. That's all.

341
00:26:25,830 --> 00:26:27,880
That doesn't mean
that my future is doomed.

342
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:30,440
If you get into a good college,

343
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:31,880
you'll have more options.

344
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,510
You'll have a brighter future too.

345
00:26:34,830 --> 00:26:35,350
Fine.

346
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:36,830
Let me tell you an example.

347
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:38,920
If we have ten laptops,

348
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,240
but there are twenty people

349
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,880
who want to play games with them.

350
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:42,920
Some people will not be able

351
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:44,160
to use the laptops, right?

352
00:26:44,750 --> 00:26:47,000
The admission quota is
very limited for good colleges.

353
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:48,920
Among the six of us,
five of us get the offer.

354
00:26:49,450 --> 00:26:50,770
I'm just giving up the good resources

355
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:52,350
for people who need it more.

356
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:54,790
However, you've just
studied hard for a while,

357
00:26:54,790 --> 00:26:56,000
but your scores surged up.

358
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:57,720
That means your efforts are recognised.

359
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:59,550
Do you want to retake it next year?

360
00:26:59,550 --> 00:27:01,110
I know of a good tuition centre.

361
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:02,110
Forget about it.

362
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:02,790
I'd rather take my own life

363
00:27:02,790 --> 00:27:04,110
than retake NCEE.

364
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:05,550
Or

365
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:07,550
you can go to college overseas?

366
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:08,640
Didn't your parents

367
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:10,200
arrange everything for you?

368
00:27:10,590 --> 00:27:11,920
That's what they want.

369
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,400
I'm not interested.

370
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:15,400
You can attend college overseas
and come back.

371
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,480
You'd become an overseas returnee, then.

372
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,440
I wanted to go, but I can't.

373
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:23,110
Do you despise me that much?

374
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:24,240
Why are you chasing me away?

375
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,200
But we'll go to college.

376
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:28,750
What about you?

377
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:31,550
If you have plans already, tell us.

378
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:34,030
Aren't we still in summer holidays?

379
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:35,830
I haven't thought about it yet.

380
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,680
Maybe I don't need to go to college.

381
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,310
I can

382
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:45,160
get a job at a cybercafe.

383
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:47,310
Or I can join Esports gaming.

384
00:27:47,590 --> 00:27:48,880
Some of you will go to Beijing,

385
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,920
some are going to Jiangzhou,

386
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,070
