387
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:53,270
I can take turns to work in your city.

388
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:55,240
I can then visit you.

389
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:56,920
Yingzi.

390
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,240
Why do you keep quiet?

391
00:27:58,510 --> 00:27:59,590
Talk some sense into him.

392
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:04,400
He has made up his mind.
What else can we say?

393
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,400
Let him be.

394
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:07,480
This is his life.

395
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:09,480
Whether he decides
to squander his life or cherish it,

396
00:28:09,790 --> 00:28:11,070
the choice is within his free will.

397
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:12,680
Enjoy.

398
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,440
I'm going home.

399
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:39,480
Mr. Huang.

400
00:28:39,480 --> 00:28:39,720
Jiang Yi.

401
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:40,440
Madam Guo.

402
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:42,640
Come on, the meal will be ready soon.

403
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:43,750
Have a seat.

404
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:44,110
Okay.

405
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:44,920
Mom.

406
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,240
What's the matter?

407
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:48,510
Why are you giving me a hard stare?

408
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:50,270
Jiang Yi's parents are back.

409
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,590
Why is he still eating with us?

410
00:28:51,590 --> 00:28:53,400
Gosh. Yingzi.

411
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:54,400
Don't listen to her, Jiang Yi.

412
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:55,750
Here, have a seat.

413
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:56,030
Okay.

414
00:28:56,030 --> 00:28:56,720
We'll eat shortly.

415
00:28:57,070 --> 00:28:58,240
Listen.

416
00:28:58,240 --> 00:29:00,030
Wang Dan can't cook.

417
00:29:00,030 --> 00:29:01,790
Didn't you know?

418
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:03,160
He's used to eating
the food we prepared.

419
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,550
Of course he's not used
to eating the food she makes.

420
00:29:04,550 --> 00:29:05,720
Am I right, Jiang Yi?

421
00:29:06,990 --> 00:29:07,710
You're right, Madam Guo.

422
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:09,440
I'm used to enjoying
good food prepared by you.

423
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,350
I can't help it now.

424
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:11,030
Thus,

425
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:12,960
if you crave for it,
just come downstairs.

426
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,440
Our dining area is your canteen.

427
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:15,920
We'll always prepare good food for you.

428
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,240
Okay. Thank you, Madam Guo.

429
00:29:17,790 --> 00:29:19,400
All right. We'll eat soon.

430
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,310
I don't like prawns.

431
00:30:21,350 --> 00:30:22,270
Hold on.

432
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:24,240
You don't like prawns?

433
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:26,510
Don't you love prawns?

434
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:27,440
I used to like it.

435
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,400
But my preferences have changed.

436
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:29,240
I don't like it anymore.

437
00:30:30,550 --> 00:30:32,310
Your preferences have changed?

438
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:33,680
You're really erratic.

439
00:30:40,550 --> 00:30:41,270
Jiang Yi.

440
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,030
Yingzi.

441
00:30:43,350 --> 00:30:44,920
Have you, along with

442
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:45,920
Mingyu and the others,

443
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:46,790
discussed

444
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:48,880
where to visit
during the summer holidays?

445
00:30:50,590 --> 00:30:51,960
We've discussed about it, Madam Guo.

446
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:53,960
We're planning to visit Jiuzhai Valley.

447
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:55,550
Jiuzhai Valley is a nice place to visit.

448
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,510
It's scenic.

449
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:58,400
I'll sponsor your trip.

450
00:30:58,640 --> 00:30:59,440
Dad.

451
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,480
I'm not going.

452
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:02,480
If I can get into
Communication University of China,

453
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,640
I'll have assignments to do
during the summer holidays.

454
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:06,880
Assignments during summer holidays?

455
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:08,310
NCEE is finally over.

456
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:10,310
Why aren't you going out
to enjoy yourself to the fullest?

457
00:31:10,310 --> 00:31:11,110
Mom.

458
00:31:11,110 --> 00:31:11,830
In high school,

459
00:31:11,830 --> 00:31:13,830
my teachers and you forced us to study.

460
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:15,200
It's different in college.

461
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:16,480
We need to study on our own.

462
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:17,590
Besides,

463
00:31:17,590 --> 00:31:20,960
I need to consider about my future.

464
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,720
How can I play every day

465
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:23,750
and make no effort at all?

466
00:31:24,270 --> 00:31:25,400
My daughter is an adult now.

467
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,480
You're so thoughtful now.

468
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,240
You and your friends

469
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:30,310
will go on separate ways in college.

470
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:31,880
You should gather more before college.

471
00:31:33,270 --> 00:31:33,830
That's right.

472
00:31:34,350 --> 00:31:35,270
Mr. Huang is right.

473
00:31:35,790 --> 00:31:36,720
I'll go to Beijing too.

474
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,440
I can still visit...

475
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:37,880
Dad.

476
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:39,440
They are my childhood friends.

477
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:41,440
But everyone has their goals.

478
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,310
Some will live a successful life,

479
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:45,550
while some will waste their life.

480
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,440
We can never gather, then.

481
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:50,550
Huang Yingzi.

482
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:52,270
You don't have
to tell me this every day.

483
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:54,160
I'm going to Beijing
not just because of you.

484
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:56,030
I'm saying all this

485
00:31:56,750 --> 00:31:58,350
not just for you.

486
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:01,550
I mean what I say.

487
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:04,440
I'm full.

488
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:29,920
Jiang Yi.

489
00:32:30,110 --> 00:32:31,000
Are you leaving so soon?

490
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:33,070
It's okay, Madam Guo.

491
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:34,960
Tell Yingzi that I'm leaving.

492
00:32:35,590 --> 00:32:36,310
I'll leave now.

493
00:32:44,560 --> 00:32:45,320
Yingzi.

494
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:47,400
I heard that you've
achieved a good score.

495
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:48,720
Congratulations.

496
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,880
It's nothing much.

497
00:32:52,920 --> 00:32:54,070
We're

498
00:32:54,480 --> 00:32:56,000
working overseas.

499
00:32:56,510 --> 00:32:57,510
We have failed

500
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:59,310
as a parent.

501
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:01,030
Thus,

502
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:03,790
I arranged for him a college in UK.

503
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:05,680
He wants to take game design

504
00:33:05,720 --> 00:33:06,830
