505
00:33:07,030 --> 00:33:07,880
However,

506
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,720
now he refuses to go overseas.

507
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,270
I know

508
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,270
he's closer

509
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:18,030
to you and the others compared to us.

510
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:20,000
I know, Madam Wang.

511
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:22,160
I'll talk to them

512
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,590
