513
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:24,480
No.

514
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,640
You're the only one who can do this.

515
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:30,270
Although all six of you
are close friends,

516
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:31,920
I know

517
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:33,240
that deep down,

518
00:33:34,110 --> 00:33:37,200
he cares about you the most.

519
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:42,640
All this while,

520
00:33:43,550 --> 00:33:45,000
thank you for taking care of Jiang Yi.

521
00:33:45,290 --> 00:33:46,730
I really appreciate it.

522
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:48,110
I can only

523
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,960
count on you now.

524
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:53,750
You don't have to do this, Madam Wang.

525
00:34:04,510 --> 00:34:05,720
Don't worry, Madam Wang.

526
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:09,710
I know what I should do.

527
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:53,840
I'm so baffled.

528
00:34:54,510 --> 00:34:56,230
Jiang was so stubborn.

529
00:34:56,230 --> 00:34:57,550
No one could persuade him.

530
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:59,360
Why did he suddenly

531
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,880
go overseas with his parents?

532
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:02,320
Zhuang Yuan.

533
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,000
It has been years.

534
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,510
Didn't you know?

535
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:08,230
I don't know.

536
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:12,630
He decided to go overseas

537
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:13,670
because of me.

538
00:35:14,670 --> 00:35:15,400
I could guess

539
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,480
that it's because of you.

540
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:17,440
However,

541
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,630
how did you convince him?

542
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:21,960
It's because of you too.

543
00:35:22,510 --> 00:35:23,190
Me?

544
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,710
Look at the word parts
of the character 'Xian'.

545
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:26,480
The right part.

546
00:35:26,550 --> 00:35:27,710
It's 'quan', isn't it?

547
00:35:28,030 --> 00:35:28,920
Remember that.

548
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,000
Come on, copy it for a few times.

549
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:37,070
Yingzi.

550
00:35:37,630 --> 00:35:38,400
Zhuang Yuan.

551
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:41,760
What are you doing?

552
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:44,360
I'm giving tuition to Madam Liu's son.

553
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:45,360
I need to meet you.

554
00:35:45,710 --> 00:35:46,630
See you half an hour later.

555
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,070
Zhuang Yuan.

556
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:02,360
Did you apply makeup again?

557
00:36:03,190 --> 00:36:03,800
Do you have a problem with that?

558
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:05,800
Never mind.

559
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:07,480
Why do you want to see me?

560
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,110
Let's take a stroll together.

561
00:36:20,710 --> 00:36:22,030
Where are we going?

562
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:27,400
Zhuang Yuan.

563
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,110
You always think

564
00:36:30,110 --> 00:36:32,190
that Jiang Yi is unambitious, don't you?

565
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:37,510
I wouldn't say that he's unambitious.

566
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:39,550
He wants to stay by your side.

567
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,000
That's considered as an ambition too.

568
00:36:42,670 --> 00:36:44,480
But one day, he told me

569
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:46,960
that he has a dream too.

570
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:48,440
What is your dream, then?

571
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,440
To be a game designer.

