00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:55,000
(I was really happy.)

573
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,070
As I thought

574
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:59,510
I'm the first person
to know about his dream.

575
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:01,360
Yingzi.

576
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:04,190
Why are you acting weirdly today?

577
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:17,760
Why are you

578
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:18,920
telling me all this?

579
00:37:42,630 --> 00:37:43,110
Let's go.

580
00:37:43,590 --> 00:37:43,880
Wait...

581
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:45,840
Why are you holding my hands?

582
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:48,150
A boy is courting me recently.

583
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:49,760
He keeps harassing me.

584
00:37:50,510 --> 00:37:51,920
Please play along and help me

585
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,230
to chase him away.

586
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:56,000
I see.

587
00:37:56,630 --> 00:37:57,630
You should tell me earlier.

588
00:38:25,230 --> 00:38:26,320
Where is he?

589
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:27,630
Don't look back.

590
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,880
He's right behind us.

591
00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:32,590
I won't look back.

592
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,190
Has he left?

593
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,030
No.

594
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:07,920
Don't look back.

595
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,030
What's wrong?

596
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,360
Why are you crying?

597
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:37,760
It's nothing.

598
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:42,000
I've got sand in my eyes.

599
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:20,840
You...

600
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:21,590
I'm sorry.

601
00:40:21,590 --> 00:40:22,670
I owe you one.

602
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:23,550
I will repay you.

603
00:40:23,550 --> 00:40:24,800
You're really something else.

604
00:40:27,230 --> 00:40:28,710
How did you bear to do that?

605
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:32,000
Of course

606
00:40:32,590 --> 00:40:33,880
I couldn't bear to do it.

607
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:36,190
But I couldn't bear

608
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:37,800
to see him acting unambitious

609
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:39,400
just to stay by my side.

610
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,000
He's so talented,

611
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,360
and smart.

612
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:45,150
I shouldn't be

613
00:40:45,150 --> 00:40:46,920
the only one recognising his merits.

614
00:40:48,110 --> 00:40:50,070
He deserves to
be acknowledged by others as well.

615
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:55,030
Won't you regret it?

616
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,320
I'd be lying if I said no.

617
00:40:59,030 --> 00:41:00,510
But I regret more

618
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:02,230
that I didn't tell him

619
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:04,150
the truth behind the incident.

620
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,590
So he still thinks

621
00:41:05,590 --> 00:41:07,360
that there's another man

622
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:08,550
between us.

623
00:41:10,590 --> 00:41:11,840
Hold on.

624
00:41:12,710 --> 00:41:14,030
Do you mean

625
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:16,670
that he still thinks
that we were a pair?

626
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,670
Well, not quite.

627
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:21,150
Gosh.

628
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:22,630
After he came back,

629
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:24,960
he acted like nothing happened.

630
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:27,230
I couldn't find a chance
to explain about it.

631
00:41:30,030 --> 00:41:30,550
No.

632
00:41:31,150 --> 00:41:33,590
You must explain this to him.

633
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,400
That's right.

634
00:41:34,590 --> 00:41:35,630
I must explain myself.

635
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:37,360
Please explain to him thoroughly.

636
00:41:37,550 --> 00:41:38,800
Explain to him thoroughly.

637
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:39,880
Give him a call.

638
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:40,590
I'll explain to him.

639
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:41,920
Yes, let me call him.

640
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:43,480
I'll ask him out now.

641
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:46,070
Why couldn't you explain it to him?

642
00:41:49,230 --> 00:41:50,000
He's picking up.

643
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,230
Isn't his phone switched off?

644
00:41:57,110 --> 00:41:58,280
You lied to me again.

645
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:01,670
Jiang.

646
00:42:08,150 --> 00:42:09,760
Why did you ask me out in a hurry?

647
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:11,000
Can't we talk about this at home?

648
00:42:12,110 --> 00:42:12,880
Home?

649
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:15,550
Which home?

650
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:24,150
I need to grab something
from his place later.

651
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:26,800
If it's nothing, I'll leave now.

652
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,150
I have something to say.

653
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:29,360
Come on.

654
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,400
Have a seat first.

655
00:42:38,590 --> 00:42:39,400
Jiang Yi.

656
00:42:40,110 --> 00:42:41,150
You ignore me on Wechat,

657
00:42:41,150 --> 00:42:42,400
and you're not returning my calls.

658
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:43,590
I have no choice

659
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:45,000
but to lure you out

660
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:46,230
through a middleman.

661
00:42:47,590 --> 00:42:48,480
Middleman?

662
00:42:48,670 --> 00:42:49,320
Me?

663
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:51,760
Fine.

664
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:52,630
Go on.

665
00:42:52,670 --> 00:42:54,030
I won't charge you both for my service.

666
00:42:56,630 --> 00:42:57,280
Sit here.

667
00:43:02,550 --> 00:43:03,230
Jiang Yi.

668
00:43:03,670 --> 00:43:05,150
I'm here to apologize to you.

669
00:43:05,550 --> 00:43:06,590
Please don't be upset.

670
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:08,400
Do you want any drinks?

671
00:43:08,400 --> 00:43:09,230
I'll order it for you.

672
00:43:12,510 --> 00:43:13,880
You're the middleman, right?

673
00:43:15,150 --> 00:43:16,360
Please tell her

674
00:43:17,070 --> 00:43:18,030
that I don't want to drink anything.

675
00:43:22,710 --> 00:43:24,070
He said he's not thirsty.

676
00:43:24,880 --> 00:43:26,360
Help me to ask him

677
00:43:26,670 --> 00:43:28,510
how long of a time
he needs to cool down.

678
00:43:33,030 --> 00:43:34,150
Yingzi said

679
00:43:34,150 --> 00:43:35,230
you shouldn't be so petty.

680
00:43:35,230 --> 00:43:36,110
Hurry up and calm down.

681
00:43:36,230 --> 00:43:37,550
I didn't say that he's petty.

682
00:43:37,550 --> 00:43:38,510
He's not petty.

683
00:43:38,760 --> 00:43:40,000
She said that you're not petty.

684
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:42,150
I'm upset with her
as she didn't keep her promise.

685
00:43:42,150 --> 00:43:42,510
He said...

686
00:43:42,510 --> 00:43:43,190
Tell him

687
00:43:43,190 --> 00:43:44,230
that it was an emergency.

688
00:43:44,230 --> 00:43:45,590
I didn't mean it.

689
00:43:45,710 --> 00:43:46,360
Hold on.

690
00:43:53,800 --> 00:43:55,150
You are sitting across each other.

691
00:43:55,150 --> 00:43:56,480
Can you talk to each other on your own?

692
00:44:03,960 --> 00:44:04,590
Jiang.

693
00:44:05,400 --> 00:44:06,840
Yingzi asked you out

694
00:44:07,030 --> 00:44:08,760
as she has something to tell you.

695
00:44:14,800 --> 00:44:15,440
Jiang Yi.

696
00:44:15,920 --> 00:44:16,880
I'm here

697
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:19,030
to apologize to you sincerely.

698
00:44:19,440 --> 00:44:20,440
If I were in your shoes,

699
00:44:20,440 --> 00:44:21,960
I'd be pissed off too.

700
00:44:22,190 --> 00:44:23,400
But I hope

701
00:44:23,480 --> 00:44:25,070
that you could give me
a chance to explain myself.

702
00:44:26,440 --> 00:44:27,590
After work,

703
00:44:28,150 --> 00:44:29,880
I saw Ding Ye at the exit.

704
00:44:30,360 --> 00:44:31,590
He pulled me into the car

705
00:44:31,590 --> 00:44:33,070
without telling me where we were going.

706
00:44:33,320 --> 00:44:34,230
In the car,

707
00:44:34,230 --> 00:44:35,440
I sent you a message immediately.

708
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:37,190
As I thought it'll end very quickly.

709
00:44:37,190 --> 00:44:38,440
I didn't expect

710
00:44:38,440 --> 00:44:39,840
that we went to a mountain.

711
00:44:39,840 --> 00:44:41,400
There's no signal in the mountain.

712
00:44:41,400 --> 00:44:43,070
Can't you leave on your own?

713
00:44:43,510 --> 00:44:44,630
You are free to leave at your own will.

714
00:44:44,630 --> 00:44:45,920
Yet, you chose to spend the night there.

715
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:51,110
I wanted to leave.

716
00:44:51,510 --> 00:44:53,280
But he said he wanted
to see the sunrise.

717
00:44:53,280 --> 00:44:54,440
I couldn't reject him.

718
00:44:54,440 --> 00:44:55,960
Why must you see the sunrise
on that day?

719
00:44:56,920 --> 00:44:57,920
Would you die if you don't?

720
00:45:04,280 --> 00:45:04,710
He...

721
00:45:04,710 --> 00:45:05,440
I got it.

722
00:45:05,840 --> 00:45:07,670
You'd tell me
that it's his personal matters.

723
00:45:07,760 --> 00:45:08,230
Am I right?

724
00:45:14,550 --> 00:45:15,590
Do you still remember, Huang Yingzi?

725
00:45:15,880 --> 00:45:16,440
Previously,

726
00:45:17,320 --> 00:45:18,150
right here,

727
00:45:18,760 --> 00:45:19,880
what you told me.

728
00:45:20,280 --> 00:45:21,920
You said you're just friends.

729
00:45:22,320 --> 00:45:23,000
Very well.

730
00:45:24,240 --> 00:45:25,760
You stood me up because of him.

731
00:45:25,960 --> 00:45:26,590
What do you mean?

732
00:45:27,360 --> 00:45:28,360
Am I not your friend, then?

733
00:45:28,710 --> 00:45:29,880
You're different.

734
00:45:29,880 --> 00:45:31,000
Yes, I can see that.

735
00:45:32,110 --> 00:45:33,190
He's more important than me.

736
00:45:33,320 --> 00:45:34,230
No, Jiang Yi.

737
00:45:34,880 --> 00:45:36,710
Can you not twist my words?

738
00:45:39,550 --> 00:45:40,960
Stop fighting.

739
00:45:41,280 --> 00:45:42,880
I'm feeling awkward here.

740
00:45:44,110 --> 00:45:44,800
Yingzi.

741
00:45:45,190 --> 00:45:46,440
You haven't changed a bit.

742
00:45:47,190 --> 00:45:48,670
You wanted Jiang to leave the country,

743
00:45:49,230 --> 00:45:50,400
so I became the scapegoat

744
00:45:50,400 --> 00:45:51,230
and the other man.

745
00:45:51,230 --> 00:45:52,880
That's not true.

746
00:45:53,320 --> 00:45:53,880
Never mind.

747
00:45:53,880 --> 00:45:55,360
I don't mind being regarded
as the other man.

748
00:45:55,800 --> 00:45:56,840
However, I hope

749
00:45:56,840 --> 00:45:57,840
that you two can have

750
00:45:57,840 --> 00:45:59,760
an open and honest conversation today

751
00:45:59,760 --> 00:46:01,440
and clear up
the misunderstandings from before.

752
00:46:04,000 --> 00:46:05,440
I've known about this all along.

753
00:46:10,480 --> 00:46:11,360
Did you know this?
